Version:          1.0
Release:          3%{?dist}%{?buildtag}
Summary:          Escalation with Overdose Control using 2 Drug Combinations

License:          GPL (>= 2)
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-rjags 
BuildRequires:    R-MASS 
Requires:         R-CRAN-rjags 
Requires:         R-MASS 

%description
Implements escalation with overdose control (EWOC) trial designs using two
drug combinations described by Tighiouart, Li and Rogatko (2017)
<doi:10.1002/sim.6961>. It calculates the recommended dose for next
cohorts and perform simulations to obtain operating characteristics.

